metadata.name: Punk Rocker Girl Aces - Standard Edition
metadata.description:
“I’m Aces…, there’s nothing that can hold me back.”

Aces is a confident girl who is very sure of herself and what she wants to achieve in life.  Despite her tenacity, she is also patient, and willing to take her time to look before she jumps into any new direction that may come her way.


Art/AnimationVFX/Script/Direction: zero-two

Music:  Raj Ramayya

Vocal Performance:  Karen Strassman

2160 x 3840 (4k Portrait Monitor Size)
